	   <tr><td colspan=2>What do you know, there IS a way to test whether or not cha affects fear!  This was an experiment for three people.  I, a level 17 cleric, a level 16 necro, and the gear from a 44 necro.  I took off all my SV magic gear, challanged the level 16 necro to a duel, and he feared me.  I timed it.  He then put on 20 points worth of cha gear.  Not only did the fear stick easier, but I ran for almost a second longer, by my calculations.  This was not a one shot try-out, but a real experiment.  I tried basically the same thing with an enchanter friend of mine, with charm, and the results were comprable.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
